<div><head>《析言論》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.2">〈析言論〉</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.3">謁者僕射季明清達，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.4">有高才，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.5">多識前代格言。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.6">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷六十二引張顯。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.7">高辛氏初生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.8">自言其名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.9">其君民終無迷謬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-1a.10">《太平御覽》卷八十、《路史‧後紀》卷九羅苹注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.2">萬雀不及一鳳皇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.3">眾星不如一月明。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.4">歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷九十二、《太平御覽》卷九百二十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.5">古諺云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.6">堯舜至聖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.7">身如脯腊；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.8">桀紂無道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.9">肥膚三尺。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.10">《太平御覽》卷三百七十八引張顯《析言》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-2a.11">又卷八十引作鄧析言。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-3a.2">〈古今訓〉</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-3a.3">土乙力為地。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1482_CHANT_001-3a.4">陸德明《爾雅‧釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
